@page "/HealthData"
@inject IHttpClientFactory HttpClientFactory
@inject NavigationManager NavigationManager

<section class="health-overview">
    <div class="titleNice">Health Overview Assessment</div>
    <div class="container1">
        <div class="text-content">
                <p class="description">
                    The first part of the Health Assessment focuses on your lifestyle and overall health, laying the groundwork for 
                    understanding how your day-to-day habits and personal health profile influence your well-being. This section plays
                     a pivotal role in creating a comprehensive picture of your current health and helps our system tailor an insurance 
                     package that truly reflects your individual needs.
                </p>
        </div>
        <div class="image-content">
                <img src="/Images/FamilyImage.png" alt="Health Assessment" class="overview-image" />   
        </div>       
    </div>
    <div class="container2">
        <div class="text-content">
                <p class="description">
                    This phase of the assessment includes a series of questions designed to evaluate key factors such as your weight, height, 
                    pregnancy status, smoking habits, and alcohol consumption. Each of these aspects contributes valuable insights into your health profile 
                    and provides the context needed to ensure that the insurance coverage you receive is aligned with your specific lifestyle. 
                    Letâ€™s delve deeper into why each element is important:
                </p>
        </div>    
    </div>
</section>

<section id="health-form" class="health-form">
    <div class="edit-medical-data-container">
    <h1 class="page-title">Health Overview</h1>
    
    <div class="info-box-medical-box">
        <div class="profile-card">
            <h2 class="section-title">Personal Information</h2>
            
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="Pregnancy">Are you currently pregnant?</label>
                <select id="pregnancy" class="form-control">
                    <option value="">Select an option</option>
                    <option value="Yes">Yes</option>
                    <option value="No">No</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="Weight">Weight (kg)</label>
                <input type="number" id="weight" class="form-control" placeholder="Enter your weight" min="0">
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="Height">Height (cm)</label>
                <input type="number" id="height" class="form-control" placeholder="Enter your height" min="0">
            </div>

            <hr />

            <h2 class="section-title">Lifestyle Habits</h2>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="Smoking">Do you smoke?</label>
                <select id="smoking" class="form-control">
                    <option value="">Select an option</option>
                    <option value="Yes">Yes</option>
                    <option value="No">No</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="Alcohol">Do you consume alcohol?</label>
                <select id="alcohol" class="form-control">
                    <option value="">Select an option</option>
                    <option value="Yes">Yes</option>
                    <option value="No">No</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary save-btn">Save Changes</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</section>